-- Japan’s Nikkei 225 Falls 20% From May 22 High
-- B y   T o m   R e d m o n d
-- 2013-06-13T02:05:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-13/japan-s-nikkei-225-falls-20-from-may-22-high.html
Japan ’s Nikkei 225 Stock Average
fell 6.3 percent to 12,456.92 as of 11:03 a.m. The gauge dropped
more than 20 percent from a May 22 high, and is poised to enter
a bear market at the close.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
